The font used on the main menu has been made by Pix3M and can be found here : https://opengameart.org/content/pixel-fonts-by-pix3m

The tileset came from LPC Winter Tiles by Demetrius :
https://opengameart.org/content/lpc-winter-tiles

... based on the following tileset from Lanea Zimmerman Extra, or William Thompson, that has also be used :
https://opengameart.org/content/lpc-modified-base-tiles

And for the beautiful snowman / main character, it has been created by Nexust (opengameart.org/users/nexust) :
https://opengameart.org/content/snowman-walk-cycle